re a long time ago.</p>\\n              <a href=\\"#\\" class=\\"inline-flex btn-themed text-lg px-8 py-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Ready?</a>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\"order-1 lg:order-2\\">\\n              <div class=\\"inspiration-image h-96 md:h-[500px]\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?w=800&amp;h=500&amp;fit=crop\\" alt=\\"Peaceful tree-lined path representing growth and inspiration\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                <div class=\\"play-button\\" onclick=\\"handlePlayClick()\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"play\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-play w-8 h-8\\"><path d=\\"M5 5a2 2 0 0 1 3.008-1.728l11.997 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\\"></path></svg>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"3"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-single-testimonial\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"5\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\\">\\n            <div class=\\"order-2 lg:order-1\\">\\n              <div class=\\"relative\\">\\n                <div class=\\"w-full h-96 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.8) 0%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.8) 50%, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.8) 100%); border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n                  <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=400&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Artem - Agency Director\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-multiply\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\"order-1 lg:order-2\\">\\n              <div class=\\"mb-8\\">\\n                <div class=\\"text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-themed-accent mb-6\\">\\"</div>\\n                <p class=\\"text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-themed-primary mb-8 leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">fullPage.js was an absolute game changer for us. It literally saved us days worth of development time, allowing us to focus on perfecting other critical aspects of our clients project.</p>\\n              </div>\\n              <div>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-2xl font-bold heading-themed mb-2\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">ARTEM</h3>\\n                <p class=\\"text-lg text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Agency Director at CodeDrips</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"5"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-photography-skills\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"11\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start lg:items-center mb-16\\">\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed mb-8 lg:mb-0\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Learn how to improve your<br>Photography skills</h2>\\n            <div class=\\"flex items-center text-themed-accent font-semibold cursor-pointer\\">\\n              <span style=\\"position: relative;\\">See all articles</span>\\n      