mollit. Exercitation veniam consequat sunt nostrud amet.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"13"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-testimonial-cards\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"19\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-16\\">\\n            <p class=\\"text-sm font-semibold text-themed-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Testimonial</p>\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Whether it''s exceptional service</h2>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\\">\\n            <!-- Testimonial Card 1 -->\\n            <div class=\\"fp-keep-color card-themed overflow-hidden\\">\\n              <div class=\\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-6\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=600&amp;h=450&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Daniel Foster\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\">\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Daniel Foster</h3>\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-center gap-1\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-star w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"><path d=\\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  <span class=\\"text-yellow-400 font-semibold\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">5.0</span>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\"text-sm text-themed-accent mb-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Sales Manager</p>\\n              <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Discover how innovative financial management solutions can transform your financial life, making it simpler and more efficient.</p>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Testimonial Card 2 -->\\n            <div class=\\"fp-keep-color card-themed overflow-hidden\\">\\n              <div class=\\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-6\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=600&amp;h=450&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Sophia Martinez\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\">\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Sophia Martinez</h3>\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-center gap-1\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-star w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"><path d=\\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  <span class=\\"text-yellow-400 font-semibold\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">5.0</span>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\"text-sm text-themed-accent mb-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Design Lead</p>\\n              <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Uncover the power of cutting-edge financial management solutions and see how they can revolutionize your financial life.</p>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Testimonial Card 3 -->\\n            <div class=\\"fp-keep-color card-themed overflow-hidden\\">\\n              <div class=\\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-6\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=600&amp;h=450&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Michael Chen\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\\">\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Michael Chen</h3>\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-center gap-1\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-star w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"><path d=\\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  <span class=\\"text-yellow-400 font-semibold\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">5.0</span>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\"text-sm text-themed-accent mb-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Product Manager</p>\\n              <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Experience simpler, more efficient ways to manage your finances, streamline your processes, and achieve your financial goals with ease.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"19"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-testimonial-carousel\\" data-testimonial-carousel=\\"\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"21\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div id=\\"testimonial-carousel-container\\" class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\\">\\n            <!-- Left side: Image -->\\n            <div class=\\"relative\\">\\n              <div class=\\"aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); position: relative;\\" data-testimonial-image-wrapper=\\"\\">\\n                <img id=\\"testimonial-carousel-image\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Customer testimonial\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Harsh P.\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Sarah Johnson\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Alex Thompson\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Emily Rodriguez\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Harsh P.\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Sarah Johnson\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Alex Thompson\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"><img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Emily Rodriguez\\" class=\\"w-full h-full object-cover\\" style=\\"position: absolute; inset: 0px; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s ease-in-out;\\" loading=\\"lazy\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Right side: Testimonial Content -->\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold heading-themed mb-6\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">What our customers are saying</h2>\\n              <p class=\\"text-xl text-themed-secondary mb-10\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Serving over 50k+ customers every month</p>\\n\\n              <!-- Navigation -->\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-center gap-6 mb-12\\">\\n                <button onclick=\\"prevTestimonialCarousel()\\" class=\\"fps-non-edit p-2 hover:bg-themed-secondary/20 rounded-lg transition-colors\\" aria-label=\\"Previous testimonial\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"arrow-left\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary\\"><path d=\\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\\"></path><path d=\\"M19 12H5\\"></path></svg>\\n                </button>\\n                <span id=\\"testimonial-carousel-counter\\" class=\\"text-lg font-semibold text-themed-accent\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">1 of 4</span>\\n                <button onclick=\\"nextTestimonialCarousel()\\" class=\\"fps-non-edit hover:bg-themed-secondary/20 rounded-lg transition-colors\\" aria-label=\\"Next testimonial\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"arrow-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\\"></path></svg>\\n                </button>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <!-- Testimonial Card -->\\n              <div id=\\"testimonial-carousel-card\\" class=\\"fp-keep-color card-themed p-8\\" style=\\"transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out; opacity: 1;\\">\\n                <!-- Rating Stars -->\\n                <div id=\\"testimonial-carousel-rating\\" class=\\"flex gap-1 mb-6\\"><i data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"></i><i data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"></i><i data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"></i><i data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"></i><i data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400\\"></i></div>\\n\\n                <!-- Testimonial Text -->\\n                <p id=\\"testimonial-carousel-text\\" class=\\"text-lg md:text-xl text-themed-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">As a busy professional, I don''t have a lot of time to manage my investments, but pagedone has made it possible for me to stay on top of my portfolio and make informed decisions quickly and easily.</p>\\n\\n                <!-- Author Info -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-center gap-3\\">\\n                  <h4 id=\\"testimonial-carousel-name\\" class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Harsh P.</h4>\\n                  <span class=\\"text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">|</span>\\n                  <p id=\\"testimonial-carousel-title\\" class=\\"text-lg\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent); position: relative;\\">Product Designer</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            \\n            <!-- Hidden testimonial items source for JS (no hardcoded data in JS) -->\\n            <div data-testimonial-items=\\"\\" class=\\"hidden\\">\\n              <div class=\\"testimonial-item\\" data-rating=\\"5\\">\\n                <img data-image=\\"\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Harsh P.\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                <div data-name=\\"\\">Harsh P.</div>\\n                <div data-title=\\"\\">Product Designer</div>\\n                <div data-text=\\"\\">As a busy professional, I don''t have a lot of time to manage my investments, but pagedone has made it possible for me to stay on top of my portfolio and make informed decisions quickly and easily.</div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"testimonial-item\\" data-rating=\\"5\\">\\n                <img data-image=\\"\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Sarah Johnson\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                <div data-name=\\"\\">Sarah Johnson</div>\\n                <div data-title=\\"\\">Marketing Director</div>\\n                <div data-text=\\"\\">The platform has exceeded all my expectations. The intuitive interface and comprehensive features have transformed how I approach my daily workflow. I couldn''t imagine working without it now.</div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"testimonial-item\\" data-rating=\\"5\\">\\n                <img data-image=\\"\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Alex Thompson\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                <div data-name=\\"\\">Alex Thompson</div>\\n                <div data-title=\\"\\">Software Engineer</div>\\n                <div data-text=\\"\\">Outstanding service and incredible attention to detail. The team truly understands what professionals need and delivers it flawlessly. This has become an essential tool in my tech stack.</div>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"testimonial-item\\" data-rating=\\"5\\">\\n                <img data-image=\\"\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?w=800&amp;h=1000&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"Emily Rodriguez\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n                <div data-name=\\"\\">Emily Rodriguez</div>\\n                <div data-title=\\"\\">Creative Director</div>\\n                <div data-text=\\"\\">I''ve tried many solutions over the years, but this one stands out for its simplicity and power. The customer support is exceptional, and the regular updates show they truly care about their users.</div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"21"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-client-feedback\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"23\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-16\\">\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold heading-themed mb-6\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Our clients feedback</h2>\\n            <p class=\\"text-xl text-themed-secondary max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">We provide all the advantage that can simplify all your financial and banking support without any further issues</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\\">\\n            <!-- Testimonial Card 1 -->\\n            <div c