yle=\\"position: relative;\\">\\"The platform has completely transformed how we manage our operations. The intuitive interface and powerful features have saved us countless hours every week, allowing us to focus on what truly matters for our business growth.\\"</p>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Donald Jackman</h3>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->\\n            <div class=\\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6\\">\\n              <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e?w=400&amp;h=500&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=face\\" alt=\\"James Washington\\" class=\\"w-full sm:w-64 h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"flex-1 flex flex-col\\">\\n                <div class=\\"flex gap-1 mb-6\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-star w-6 h-6 fill-orange-500 text-orange-500\\"><path d=\\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"star\\" class=\\"lucide l