6\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">See it, build it, test it, do it</h2>\\n              <p class=\\"text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">The best thing about our platform is discovering new things and ideas from people all over the world.</p>\\n              <a href=\\"#\\" class=\\"inline-flex btn-themed text-lg px-8 py-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Explore Now</a>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"60"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-rotated-images\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"background-color: var(--secondary-bg);\\" data-section=\\"61\\" data-bg=\\"default\\" data-original-bg=\\"\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\\">\\n            <!-- Left Side - Text Content -->\\n            <div class=\\"order-2 lg:order-1\\">\\n              <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">We work to make our products more sustainable every day</h2>\\n              <a href=\\"#\\" class=\\"inline-flex text-lg px-8 py-4 btn-themed-outline\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">+ INFO</a>\\n            </div>\\n            <!-- Right Side - Three Images -->\\n            <div class=\\"order-1 lg:order-2 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4\\">\\n              <div class=\\"transform rotate-2\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=300&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\\" alt=\\"Sustainability 1\\" class=\\"w-full h-64 object-cover shadow-lg\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"transform -rotate-1 mt-8\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?w=300&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\\" alt=\\"Sustainability 2\\" class=\\"w-full h-64 object-cover shadow-lg\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\"transform rotate-1 mt-4\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527219525722-f9767a7f2884?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=300&amp;h=400&amp;q=80\\" alt=\\"Sustainability 3\\" class=\\"w-full h-64 object-cover shadow-lg\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"61"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-features-accordion\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" data-acc=\\"\\" data-acc-auto-open=\\"true\\" data-section=\\"69\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start\\">\\n            <!-- Left Side - Accordion -->\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed mb-12\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Significant others</h2>\\n              \\n              <div class=\\"space-y-4\\" id=\\"features-accordion\\">\\n                <!-- Feature 1 - Expanded by default -->\\n                <div class=\\"rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"w-full p-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer\\">\\n                    <span class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">iPhone and Mac</span>\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"chevron-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary transition-transform duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"rotate-90\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer; transform: rotate(90deg);\\"><path d=\\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 128px;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"px-6 pb-6\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Seamlessly integrate your iPhone with your Mac for a unified experience. Share files instantly, take calls on your Mac, and use your iPhone as a webcam. Universal Clipboard lets you copy on one device and paste on another.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Feature 2 -->\\n                <div class=\\"fp-keep-color bg-themed-secondary rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"w-full p-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer\\">\\n                    <span class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">iPhone and Apple Watch</span>\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"chevron-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary transition-transform duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"rotate-90\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\"><path d=\\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"px-6 pb-6\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Misplaced your iPhone? The latest Apple Watch models can show you its approximate distance and direction. To set up a group photo on your iPhone, join the group and use Apple Watch as a viewfinder to snap the shot. And when you take a call on your Apple Watch, just tap your iPhone to continue the conversation there.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Feature 3 -->\\n                <div class=\\"fp-keep-color bg-themed-secondary rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"w-full p-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer\\">\\n                    <span class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">iPhone and AirPods</span>\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"chevron-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary transition-transform duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"rotate-90\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\"><path d=\\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"px-6 pb-6\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Experience crystal-clear audio with seamless switching between devices. Spatial audio creates an immersive listening experience, while active noise cancellation blocks out distractions. Conversation Boost makes voices clearer in crowded environments.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Feature 4 -->\\n                <div class=\\"fp-keep-color bg-themed-secondary rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"w-full p-6 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer\\">\\n                    <span class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">iPhone and iPad</span>\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"chevron-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-6 h-6 text-themed-primary transition-transform duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"rotate-90\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\"><path d=\\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"px-6 pb-6\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Start a project on your iPhone and finish it on your iPad with Handoff. Use your iPad as a second display with Sidecar. Draw with Apple Pencil and insert sketches directly into documents on your iPhone.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Right Side - Visual -->\\n            <div class=\\"lg:sticky lg:top-20\\">\\n              <div class=\\"relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1691256676376-357c3aa66c89?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80&amp;w=1760\\" alt=\\"Device ecosystem\\" class=\\"w-full h-auto object-cover\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"69"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-product-slider\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center bg-themed-secondary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"70\\" data-bg=\\"secondary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-secondary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"w-full py-20\\">\\n          <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\\">\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Explore the lineup.</h2>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <div class=\\"relative\\">\\n            <div class=\\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl mx-4 sm:mx-6 lg:mx-8\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); background: var(--bg-themed-secondary);\\">\\n              <div data-product-slider=\\"\\" class=\\"flex gap-8 overflow-x-auto p-12 scroll-smooth\\" style=\\"scrollbar-width: none; -ms-overflow-style: none;\\">\\n                <!-- Product 1 -->\\n                <div class=\\"fp-keep-color flex-shrink-0 bg-themed-primary p-8 rounded-3xl\\" style=\\"width: 372px; border-radius: var(--card-radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"mb-6 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"background: linear-gradient