osition: relative;\\">Our platform provides automated tracking capabilities designed to streamline and simplify your business operations. By automating.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Feature 3: AI Advisor -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6 relative\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 p-4 rounded-2xl relative z-10\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"user-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-user-circle w-6 h-6\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"10\\" r=\\"3\\"></circle><path d=\\"M7 20.662V19a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1.662\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-2xl font-bold heading-themed mb-3\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">AI Advisor</h3>\\n                    <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">This AI is not just a mere tool but a sophisticated companion that sifts through vast amounts of data to offer you personalized recommendations.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Feature 4: Schedule Tracking -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6 relative\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 p-4 rounded-2xl relative z-10\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"calendar-clock\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-calendar-clock w-6 h-6\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><path d=\\"M16 14v2.2l1.6 1\\"></path><path d=\\"M16 2v4\\"></path><path d=\\"M21 7.5V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h3.5\\"></path><path d=\\"M3 10h5\\"></path><path d=\\"M8 2v4\\"></path><circle cx=\\"16\\" cy=\\"16\\" r=\\"6\\"></circle></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-2xl font-bold heading-themed mb-3\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Schedule Tracking</h3>\\n                    <p class=\\"text-themed-secondary leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Whether you''re managing personal appointments, work deadlines, or social engagements, this schedule tracking capability acts as your reliable.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"102"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-interactive-features\\" class=\\"min-h-screen bg-themed-primary has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"max-height: 100dvh; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 3rem 0;\\" data-section=\\"104\\" data-bg=\\"primary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-primary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex-1 overflow-y: auto;\\">\\n          <!-- Heading -->\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-16\\">\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed mb-4\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Make your payment transaction</h2>\\n            <p class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\"><span class=\\"text-themed-accent\\">Easy</span> and <span class=\\"text-themed-accent\\">Professional</span></p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Feature Tabs -->\\n          <div class=\\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12\\">\\n            <button class=\\"feature-tab active px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3\\" data-tab=\\"release\\" onclick=\\"switchFeatureTab(''release'')\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--button-radius); position: relative;\\"><svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"grid-3x3\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-grid-3x3 w-5 h-5\\"><rect width=\\"18\\" height=\\"18\\" x=\\"3\\" y=\\"3\\" rx=\\"2\\"></rect><path d=\\"M3 9h18\\"></path><path d=\\"M3 15h18\\"></path><path d=\\"M9 3v18\\"></path><path d=\\"M15 3v18\\"></path></svg>Release Confidently</button>\\n            <button class=\\"feature-tab px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3\\" data-tab=\\"analytic\\" onclick=\\"switchFeatureTab(''analytic'')\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--button-radius); position: relative;\\"><svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"bar-chart-2\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-bar-chart-2 w-5 h-5\\"><path d=\\"M5 21v-6\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 21V3\\"></path><path d=\\"M19 21V9\\"></path></svg>Powerful Analytic</button>\\n            <button class=\\"feature-tab px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3\\" data-tab=\\"report\\" onclick=\\"switchFeatureTab(''report'')\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--button-radius); position: relative;\\"><svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"presentation\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-presentation w-5 h-5\\"><path d=\\"M2 3h20\\"></path><path d=\\"M21 3v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V3\\"></path><path d=\\"m7 21 5-5 5 5\\"></path></svg>Live Project Report</button>\\n            <button class=\\"feature-tab px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-3\\" data-tab=\\"case\\" onclick=\\"switchFeatureTab(''case'')\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--button-radius); position: relative;\\"><svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"book-open\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-book-open w-5 h-5\\"><path d=\\"M12 7v14\\"></path><path d=\\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\\"></path></svg>Case Study</button>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Feature Description -->\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-12\\">\\n            <p id=\\"feature-description\\" class=\\"text-xl text-themed-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Trusted in more than 100 countries and 5 million customers. Transact easily and quickly with just one click.</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Feature Images -->\\n          <div class=\\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\\">\\n            <div class=\\"relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n              <img id=\\"feature-image\\" src=\\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=1200&amp;h=700&amp;fit=crop\\" alt=\\"Dashboard preview\\" class=\\"w-full h-auto transition-opacity duration-300\\" style=\\"\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"104"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-standout-features\\" class=\\"min-h-screen bg-themed-secondary has-bg-image section\\" data-section=\\"105\\" data-bg=\\"secondary\\" data-original-bg=\\"bg-themed-secondary\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start\\">\\n            <!-- Left: Content Wrapper -->\\n            <div class=\\"lg:sticky lg:top-24\\">\\n              <div class=\\"max-w-lg p-10 rounded-3xl fp-keep-color\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg); border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\">\\n                <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold heading-themed mb-6\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">How we stand out in world</h2>\\n                <p class=\\"text-xl text-themed-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Offering unique features and benefits that are tailored to your needs.</p>\\n                <a href=\\"#\\" class=\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold transition-colors\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent); position: relative;\\">Contact us\\n<svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"arrow-right\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\\"></path></svg></a>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Right: Features Grid -->\\n            <div class=\\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\\">\\n              <!-- Feature 1: Specific Tools -->\\n              <div class=\\"p-6\\">\\n                <div class=\\"mb-4\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"edit-3\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-edit-3 w-5 h-5\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><path d=\\"M13 21h8\\"></path><path d=\\"M21.174 6.812a1 1 0 0 0-3.986-3.987L3.842 16.174a2 2 0 0 0-.5.83l-1.321 4.352a.5.5 0 0 0 .623.622l4.353-1.32a2 2 0 0 0 .83-.497z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed mb-2\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Specific Tools</h3>\\n                <p class=\\"text-base text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Experience the power of our specific tools, which are tailored to your needs.</p>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <!-- Feature 2: Implementation Examples -->\\n              <div class=\\"p-6\\">\\n                <div class=\\"mb-4\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"key\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-key w-5 h-5\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><path d=\\"m15.5 7.5 2.3 2.3a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l2.1-2.1a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.4L19 4\\"></path><path d=\\"m21 2-9.6 9.6\\"></path><circle cx=\\"7.5\\" cy=\\"15.5\\" r=\\"5.5\\"></circle></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed mb-2\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Implementation Examples</h3>\\n                <p class=\\"text-base text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Real examples provide you with valuable insights to optimize use of our platform.</p>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <!-- Feature 3: Practical Information -->\\n              <div class=\\"p-6\\">\\n                <div class=\\"mb-4\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"inbox\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-inbox w-5 h-5\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><polyline points=\\"22 12 16 12 14 15 10 15 8 12 2 12\\"></polyline><path d=\\"M5.45 5.11 2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed mb-2\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Practical Information</h3>\\n                <p class=\\"text-base text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Information designed to help you navigate the complex data problems.</p>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <!-- Feature 4: Exchange of Experience -->\\n              <div class=\\"p-6\\">\\n                <div class=\\"mb-4\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"inline-flex p-3 rounded-xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--accent-bg);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"message-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-message-circle w-5 h-5\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-accent);\\"><path d=\\"M2.992 16.342a2 2 0 0 1 .094 1.167l-1.065 3.29a1 1 0 0 0 1.236 1.168l3.413-.998a2 2 0 0 1 1.099.092 10 10 0 1 0-4.777-4.719\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold heading-themed mb-2\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Exchange of Experience</h3>\\n                <p class=\\"text-base text-themed-secondary\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">Provides you with access to experts and pro''s knowledge in your community.</p>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"105"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-faq-image\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-bg);\\" data-acc=\\"\\" data-acc-auto-open=\\"false\\" data-section=\\"110\\" data-bg=\\"default\\" data-original-bg=\\"\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 py-24\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\\">\\n            <!-- Left Side - FAQs -->\\n            <div>\\n              <p class=\\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Question &amp; Answer</p>\\n              <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-12\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Most Asked Question</h2>\\n\\n              <!-- FAQ List -->\\n              <div class=\\"space-y-6\\">\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->\\n                <div class=\\"cursor-pointer border-b pb-6 transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"border-color: var(--border-color);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I update my billing information?</h3>\\n                    <div class=\\"w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"plus-minus\\">\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"plus\\" data-icon-plus=\\"\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-plus\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 5v14\\"></path></svg>\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"minus\\" data-icon-minus=\\"\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-minus hidden\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path></svg>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"mt-4\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-base leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To update your billing information, log in and go to the billing or payment page. Look for an option to \\"Update payment method\\" or \\"Edit billing information\\" and follow the prompts. Be sure to save your changes before exiting.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->\\n                <div class=\\"cursor-pointer border-b pb-6 transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"border-color: var(--border-color);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I delete my account?</h3>\\n                    <div class=\\"w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"plus-minus\\">\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"plus\\" data-icon-plus=\\"\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-plus\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 5v14\\"></path></svg>\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"minus\\" data-icon-minus=\\"\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-minus hidden\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path></svg>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"mt-4\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-base leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Visit your account settings and look for the \\"Delete Account\\" option. This action is permanent and will remove all your data. We recommend downloading any important information before proceeding with account deletion.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->\\n                <div class=\\"cursor-pointer border-b pb-6 transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"border-color: var(--border-color);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I join a group or community?</h3>\\n                    <div class=\\"w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"plus-minus\\">\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"plus\\" data-icon-plus=\\"\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-plus\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 5v14\\"></path></svg>\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"minus\\" data-icon-minus=\\"\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-minus hidden\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path></svg>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"mt-4\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-base leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Navigate to the Communities section and browse available groups. Click \\"Join\\" on any community that interests you. Some groups may require approval from administrators before you can participate.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->\\n                <div class=\\"cursor-pointer border-b pb-6 transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"border-color: var(--border-color);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How can I contact customer support?</h3>\\n                    <div class=\\"w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"plus-minus\\">\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"plus\\" data-icon-plus=\\"\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-plus\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 5v14\\"></path></svg>\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"minus\\" data-icon-minus=\\"\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-minus hidden\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path></svg>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"mt-4\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-base leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Our customer support team is available 24/7 via email, live chat, or phone. You can access support through the Help button in your dashboard or visit our support center at support.example.com.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->\\n                <div class=\\"cursor-pointer border-b pb-6 transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"border-color: var(--border-color);\\" data-acc-item=\\"\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4\\" style=\\"cursor: pointer;\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Which is better short term or long term?</h3>\\n                    <div class=\\"w-6 h-6 flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300\\" data-acc-icon=\\"plus-minus\\">\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"plus\\" data-icon-plus=\\"\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-plus\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 5v14\\"></path></svg>\\n                      <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"minus\\" data-icon-minus=\\"\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-minus hidden\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M5 12h14\\"></path></svg>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div data-acc-content=\\"\\" class=\\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out\\" style=\\"max-height: 0;\\">\\n                    <div class=\\"mt-4\\">\\n                      <p class=\\"text-base leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">The choice depends on your goals and financial situation. Short-term plans offer flexibility, while long-term plans often provide better value and stability. Contact our advisors for personalized recommendations.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Right Side - Image -->\\n            <div class=\\"relative\\">\\n              <div class=\\"rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\\" style=\\"box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"./public/images/workspace.jpg\\" alt=\\"Workspace dashboard illustration\\" class=\\"w-full h-auto object-cover\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <!-- Decorative element -->\\n              <div class=\\"absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-48 h-48 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"110"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-faq-visible\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-bg);\\" data-section=\\"111\\" data-bg=\\"default\\" data-original-bg=\\"\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 py-24\\">\\n          <div class=\\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start\\">\\n            <!-- Left Side - FAQs -->\\n            <div>\\n              <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-12\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Frequently Asked Question</h2>\\n\\n              <!-- FAQ List -->\\n              <div class=\\"space-y-8 mb-12\\">\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex gap-6\\">\\n                  <!-- Circular Bullet with Question Mark -->\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-6 h-6 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How can I contact customer support?</h3>\\n                    <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To contact customer support, look for a \\"Contact us\\" or \\"Help\\" button or link on the website or platform. You may be able to email, call, or chat with customer support for assistance.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex gap-6\\">\\n                  <!-- Circular Bullet with Question Mark -->\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-6 h-6 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How can I reset my password?</h3>\\n                    <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Go to the login page and click on the \\"Forgot password\\" link. Enter the email associated with your account, and you will receive an email with instructions on how to reset your password.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex gap-6\\">\\n                  <!-- Circular Bullet with Question Mark -->\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                    <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-6 h-6 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                    <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I change my privacy settings?</h3>\\n                    <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To change your privacy settings, log in and go to the settings or account page. Look for an option to \\"Privacy\\" or \\"Security\\" and follow the instructions.</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n\\n              <!-- View All FAQs Button -->\\n              <button class=\\"btn-themed px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\">View All FAQs</button>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- Right Side - Image -->\\n            <div class=\\"relative lg:sticky lg:top-24\\">\\n              <div class=\\"rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\\" style=\\"box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\\">\\n                <img src=\\"./public/images/business-team.jpg\\" alt=\\"Customer support representative\\" class=\\"w-full h-auto object-cover\\" style=\\"border-radius: var(--card-radius);\\" loading=\\"lazy\\">\\n              </div>\\n              <!-- Decorative element -->\\n              <div class=\\"absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"111"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-faq-hover\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-bg);\\" data-section=\\"112\\" data-bg=\\"default\\" data-original-bg=\\"\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 py-24\\">\\n          <!-- Header -->\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-16\\">\\n            <p class=\\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Most asked questions</p>\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Questions &amp; Answers</h2>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- FAQ Grid -->\\n          <div class=\\"fp-keep-color grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto\\">\\n            <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->\\n            <div class=\\"card-themed-thin\\">\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6\\">\\n                <!-- Icon -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-7 h-7 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                </div>\\n                <!-- Content -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                  <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I find my purchase history?</h3>\\n                  <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">First log in and go to the account or purchase history page. Look for a list of your past purchases or orders, and click on any item to see more details.</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->\\n            <div class=\\"card-themed-thin\\">\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6\\">\\n                <!-- Icon -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-7 h-7 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                </div>\\n                <!-- Content -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                  <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I change my privacy settings?</h3>\\n                  <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To change your privacy settings, log in and go to the settings or account page. Look for an option to \\"Privacy\\" or \\"Security\\" and follow the instructions.</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->\\n            <div class=\\"card-themed-thin\\">\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6\\">\\n                <!-- Icon -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-7 h-7 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                </div>\\n                <!-- Content -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                  <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I change my email address?</h3>\\n                  <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To change your email address, log in and go to the settings or account page. Look for an option to \\"Change email\\" or \\"Edit account information\\" and follow the prompts. Be sure to save your changes before exiting.</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n\\n            <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->\\n            <div class=\\"card-themed-thin\\">\\n              <div class=\\"flex items-start gap-6\\">\\n                <!-- Icon -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                  <svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"help-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-help-circle w-7 h-7 text-white\\"><circle cx=\\"12\\" cy=\\"12\\" r=\\"10\\"></circle><path d=\\"M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3\\"></path><path d=\\"M12 17h.01\\"></path></svg>\\n                </div>\\n                <!-- Content -->\\n                <div class=\\"flex-1\\">\\n                  <h3 class=\\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">How do I update my profile information?</h3>\\n                  <p class=\\"text-sm leading-relaxed transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">To update your profile information, log in and go to the profile or account page. Look for an option to \\"Edit profile\\" or \\"Update information\\" and follow the prompts. Be sure to save your changes before exiting.</p>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>","number":"112"},{"html":"<section id=\\"fp-theme-pricing-toggle\\" class=\\"min-h-screen flex items-center has-bg-image section\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-bg);\\" data-section=\\"113\\" data-bg=\\"default\\" data-original-bg=\\"\\">\\n        <div class=\\"fp-bg\\"></div>\\n        <div class=\\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 py-24\\">\\n          <!-- Header -->\\n          <div class=\\"text-center mb-12\\">\\n            <h2 class=\\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Flexible Pricing Plans to Suit You</h2>\\n            <p class=\\"text-lg mb-8\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">No commitment. No hidden charges</p>\\n            \\n            <!-- Toggle Switch -->\\n            <div class=\\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4\\">\\n              <span data-pricing-monthly=\\"\\" class=\\"text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); position: relative;\\">Monthly</span>\\n              <button data-pricing-toggle=\\"\\" class=\\"fps-non-edit relative w-16 h-8 rounded-full transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--primary-accent);\\">\\n                <span data-pricing-slider=\\"\\" class=\\"fps-non-edit absolute top-1 left-1 w-6 h-6 bg-white rounded-full shadow-md transition-transform duration-300\\"></span>\\n              </button>\\n              <span data-pricing-yearly=\\"\\" class=\\"text-lg font-semibold transition-colors duration-300\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">Yearly</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- Pricing Cards -->\\n          <div class=\\"fp-keep-color grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto\\">\\n            <!-- Free Plan -->\\n            <div class=\\"rounded-3xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300\\" style=\\"background: var(--secondary-bg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);\\">\\n              <!-- Card Image -->\\n              <div class=\\"h-48 relative overflow-hidden\\" style=\\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\\">\\n                <div class=\\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"w-32 h-32 rounded-lg transform rotate-12\\" style=\\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\\"></div>\\n                </div>\\n              </div>\\n              \\n              <!-- Card Content -->\\n              <div class=\\"p-8\\">\\n                <div class=\\"mb-6\\">\\n                  <div class=\\"flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2\\">\\n                    <span class=\\"text-5xl font-bold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); position: relative;\\">$0</span>\\n                    <span class=\\"text-lg\\" style=\\"color: var(--secondary-text); position: relative;\\">/ <span class=\\"pricing-period\\">Month</span></span>\\n                  </div>\\n                  <h3 class=\\"text-2xl font-bold\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text); font-family: var(--heading-font); position: relative;\\">Free Plan</h3>\\n                </div>\\n\\n                <!-- Features -->\\n                <ul class=\\"space-y-4 mb-8\\">\\n                  <li class=\\"flex items-start gap-3\\" style=\\"position: relative;\\"><svg xmlns=\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\" width=\\"24\\" height=\\"24\\" viewBox=\\"0 0 24 24\\" fill=\\"none\\" stroke=\\"currentColor\\" stroke-width=\\"2\\" stroke-linecap=\\"round\\" stroke-linejoin=\\"round\\" data-lucide=\\"check-circle\\" class=\\"lucide lucide-check-circle w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\"><path d=\\"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335\\"></path><path d=\\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\\"></path></svg>\\n<p><span class=\\"text-base\\" style=\\"color: var(--primary-text);\\">AI Advisor</span></p></li>\\n                  <li class=\\"flex items-start gap-3\\" style=\\"p